<h2>FAQ deep dives</h2>
<p><strong>What is the best stack for Shopify welcome series?</strong> Privy/Justuno capture with source tags, Sequenzy branched welcome execution, Klaviyo for complex segmentation, Yotpo proof in email two, Postscript SMS only with opt-in after email silence. Stack operators should document this answer in internal runbooks — not rely on tribal knowledge when agencies turn over.</p>
